rting at 00:00:50 with Infantino saying \"we are now going to do the draw.\"\n\nTherefore, the evidence does not support a preponderance standard that the \"Ronaldo\" statements were made \"during the FIFA World Cup Draw\" as defined by the market.\n\nSince the plaintiff has not proven by a preponderance of evidence that the statements were made during the market's specified time period, I should vote \"not_demonstrated\".\n\nLet's check the requirements for the response:\n- I need to call aar_submit_council_vote\n- Vote should be \"not_demonstrated\"\n- Rationale must be concise (no more than three sentences)\n\nRationale: The transcript evidence explicitly identifies Trump's Ronaldo mentions as occurring in remarks \"Prior to the 2026 FIFA World Cup Draw,\" and the formal draw transcript contains no Ronaldo mention. The market terms do not include pre-event press exchanges as part of \"during\" the specific event of the Draw.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e784db7adc9340fcac5325","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_submit_council_vote","args":"{\""},"partialArgs":"{\"tool\": \"aar_submit_council_vote\", \"args\": \"{\\\"","streamIndex":0}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"qwen/qwen3-next-80b-a3b-thinking","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782762194999,"responseId":"gen-1782762195-IAAm4VEIvCT04Kf5K5V9","responseModel":"qwen/qwen3-next-80b-a3b-thinking-2509"}},"message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to analyze the case thoroughly. This is an arbitration case about a Kalshi market where the question is whether Trump said \"Ronaldo\" during the FIFA World Cup Draw.\n\nLet me understand the core issue:\n- Market title: \"What will Trump say during the FIFA World Cup Draw?\"\n- Strike: \"Ronaldo\"\n- The dispute is whether Trump 