arting at 00:00:50 with Infantino saying \"we are now going to do the draw.\"\n\nTherefore, the evidence does not support a preponderance standard that the \"Ronaldo\" statements were made \"during the FIFA World Cup Draw\" as defined by the market.\n\nSince the plaintiff has not proven by a preponderance of evidence that the statements were made during the market's specified time period, I should vote \"not_demonstrated\".\n\nLet's check the requirements for the response:\n- I need to call aar_submit_council_vote\n- Vote should be \"not_demonstrated\"\n- Rationale must be concise (no more than three sentences)\n\nRationale: The transcript evidence explicitly identifies Trump's Ronaldo mentions as occurring in remarks \"Prior to the 2026 FIFA World Cup Draw,\" and the formal draw transcript contains no Ronaldo mention. The market terms do not include pre-event press exchanges as part of \"during\" the specific event of the Draw.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e784db7adc9340fcac5325","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_submit_council_vote","args":"{\"vote\":\"not_demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\"Transcript evidence explicitly identifies Ronaldo mentions as occurring in remarks 'Prior to' the event, while the formal draw transcript contains no Ronaldo reference. Market terms require"},"partialArgs":"{\"tool\": \"aar_submit_council_vote\", \"args\": \"{\\\"vote\\\":\\\"not_demonstrated\\\",\\\"rationale\\\":\\\"Transcript evidence explicitly identifies Ronaldo mentions as occurring in remarks 'Prior to' the event, while the formal draw transcript contains no Ronaldo reference. Market terms require","streamIndex":0}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"qwen/qwen3-next-80b-a3b-thinking","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782762194999,"responseId":"gen-1782762195-IAAm4VEIvCT0